Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.34,0:01:21.89,Hardsub,,0,0,200,,#anime-faith@irc.chatspike.net\N#miyuki-no-tamari@irc.chatspike.net
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.01,0:01:20.43,Hardsub,,0,0,10,,{\an8}sasaykana koi ga hajimaru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.01,0:01:20.43,Hardsub,,0,0,10,,my little love is starting now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.68,0:01:26.98,Hardsub,,0,0,50,,Mischievous Spring Breeze
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.55,0:01:53.67,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.18,0:02:01.10,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,It's the new semester, and I'm late already!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.43,0:02:02.64,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:03.81,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tsuyoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:05.72,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,We're in the same class this semester.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:07.64,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Let's have fun again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.27,0:02:09.44,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.15,0:02:13.77,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You're too cold, Tsuyoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.86,0:02:15.03,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.36,0:02:17.70,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.37,0:02:21.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:27.25,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,See ya there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.54,0:02:28.37,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Su-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.88,0:02:39.38,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.72,0:02:45.06,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,If you don't hurry, you'll be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.06,0:02:46.56,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:56.11,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,It looks like it can't get down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.73,0:02:59.70,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Cats are good at jumping from high places.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:01.86,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.45,0:03:04.49,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,She sounds so scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:05.58,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.99,0:03:06.37,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:17.00,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.42,0:03:17.92,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Come to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:20.88,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:22.93,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.09,0:03:24.51,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Come 'ere!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.93,0:03:28.27,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You know, you ruined my breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.64,0:03:30.35,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:39.36,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Don't climb up there again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.11,0:03:42.32,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Thank you,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.57,0:03:45.66,Hardsub,,0,0,10,,{\an8\fs26}Notes: "Senpai" is used to refer to someone more experienced. For example, an upperclassmen or an experienced co-worker.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.57,0:03:43.53,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Yamaguchi-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:45.66,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You know who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.13,0:04:00.55,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:01.55,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,There's blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:04.93,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,It's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.72,0:04:08.60,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,But if it gets infected...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.49,0:04:23.49,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,All done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:29.83,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,The cat seems to like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:30.66,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:32.16,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Ah, anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:33.54,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What are we going to do with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:35.92,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What shall we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:50.47,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,My, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.22,0:04:52.73,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.18,0:04:53.89,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,We're gonna be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.18,0:04:54.60,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Let's run!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:55.35,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:01.11,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.90,0:05:06.57,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.07,0:05:08.74,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Tsuyoshi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:10.66,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,It's the start of the semester and\Nyou're on a date already?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.83,0:05:12.75,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Minatsu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.04,0:05:13.91,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Good timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:20.59,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Ugh... I can't run anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:23.51,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Whew.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.01,0:05:25.55,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I'm just in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:33.02,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Minatsu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:36.06,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Tsuyoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:43.44,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Why is {\i1}that{\i0} guy with Minatsu-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.11,0:05:48.61,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You really saved us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.03,0:05:51.08,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I'm really, really grateful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:54.08,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Shall I take you to school everyday, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:55.08,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.54,0:05:58.25,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,But you'll have to pay transportation fees.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.09,0:06:05.26,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Well then, when you come to work,\Nclean up the store for me, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:05.96,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.13,0:06:07.01,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Do I have to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.59,0:06:08.84,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.18,0:06:11.01,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You're so mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.06,0:06:22.98,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Morning, Miko-chan, Mizuho!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:24.23,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Tsuyoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.57,0:06:25.90,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,So you're not late today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:29.57,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I hope it doesn't rain later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:31.20,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Miko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:32.87,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Let's have a date next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.53,0:06:34.24,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.04,0:06:38.46,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What's with the handkerchief?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.62,0:06:39.92,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:41.29,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Oh... This...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.79,0:06:44.42,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,It's a magic item so girls keep off me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.09,0:06:45.71,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.09,0:06:46.96,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.26,0:06:51.84,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I'll also do some magic too, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:54.81,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.39,0:06:57.56,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,We'll tie all of these, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:07:01.77,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I think the magic will definitely work very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:02.86,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.11,0:07:04.65,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Let's continue next time. I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.15,0:07:07.65,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.19,0:07:10.82,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I'll tie this for Mizuho.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:11.78,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.95,0:07:13.37,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Next time, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:19.50,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Both of them are awfully polite, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:29.92,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,So, this is the new classroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:31.43,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,OH!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:33.55,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of cute girls in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.26,0:07:37.06,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Oh my...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:38.10,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Shindou Reiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:39.52,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,She's going to be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.81,0:07:40.60,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.93,0:07:44.65,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Don't start flirting with the new girls already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.86,0:07:45.19,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:46.52,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,There's a beauty right here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.69,0:07:48.32,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:53.32,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Ugh... I finally made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:55.62,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Hey, Minoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.82,0:07:57.37,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Be a little more punctual, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:07:58.62,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.95,0:08:01.21,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,There are quite a few girls of your type in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:06.04,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I'm stuck with you two again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.30,0:08:11.38,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I hope you don't pull the class average down once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:15.30,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,W-W-W-What do you mean by that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.05,0:08:19.06,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I wonder what that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.56,0:08:22.43,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Figure it out as a homework assignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.53,0:08:30.19,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Well, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:32.82,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,This is your final year in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:39.03,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I wish you all a fulfilling study and sports life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.79,0:08:42.96,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,We're pretty lucky to have Mitsuki-sensei\Nas homeroom teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.37,0:08:46.12,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you're into older women?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.96,0:08:48.25,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,It depends on the person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:49.63,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You two, over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:52.67,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Don't waste your youth talking crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.63,0:08:54.34,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:08:56.13,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.76,0:08:59.47,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Is it okay to use our youth for love?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:00.56,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,If you can...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.89,0:09:03.48,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Though I hope you save some for studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.06,0:09:05.64,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,So Tsuyoshi,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:06.85,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,you'd better remember that well!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.19,0:09:08.90,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Why are you telling me that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.39,0:09:47.44,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Yamaguchi-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.81,0:09:49.02,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,is in class C!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.15,0:09:50.77,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.23,0:09:53.11,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Miyuki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:56.28,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,The beautiful detective, Iijima Miyuki, appears!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:09:58.66,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You were behind me all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:00.03,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,More or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.33,0:10:03.04,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,And so what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:05.08,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You have some moves there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:07.00,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Umm... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:09.42,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,All the classrooms changed...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.71,0:10:10.42,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.59,0:10:13.25,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You got lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:13.96,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:15.05,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.63,0:10:16.47,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.34,0:10:19.09,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You like Yamaguchi-senpai, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.55,0:10:20.14,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:21.51,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,No-Nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:30.23,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I'm Satake Haruhiko of class 3-C.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:32.48,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I want to tell your eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.69,0:10:34.02,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,"I love you."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.74,0:10:45.12,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,This hand will never forget the\Nwarmth of your shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.74,0:10:50.92,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Of course, who would blame a girl\Nfor running shyly from my beauty?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.72,0:11:02.34,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Ai, you really hate guys, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.64,0:11:06.26,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You never talk to any of the guys in our class.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:10.85,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,But you spoke to Yamaguchi-senpai this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:13.44,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,It's okay if it's senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:15.82,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,It's because there was a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:17.32,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Ai...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:18.78,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Could it be that you really...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.20,0:11:24.03,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you, don't get involved with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.49,0:11:27.29,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Rumor has it that he's been with many girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.41,0:11:30.04,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.91,0:11:32.83,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I was supposed to go help the teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.33,0:11:34.50,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Ai, we'll talk later, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:37.88,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:39.59,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I still...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:52.27,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.94,0:11:55.36,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,That must be a love letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.06,0:11:56.44,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.86,0:11:57.94,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,It's a new semester.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:11:59.78,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Someone is already confessing their love for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:01.61,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Geez, I'm so envious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:03.53,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:04.41,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What's with that look?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:12.87,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You'd better find somewhere quiet\Nto read that kinda thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:15.25,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.46,0:12:20.80,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Tsuyoshi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:22.42,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I wonder what he's up to~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:26.51,Hardsub,,20,0,10,,{\an7}For fans, by fans
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.60,0:12:29.89,Hardsub,,20,0,10,,{\an7}Not for sale or rent
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:41.61,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Tsuyoshi-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:43.65,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I really like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.91,0:12:45.57,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Today, at 5 PM,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.03,0:12:47.78,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting for you at the Uzukigidou Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.45,0:12:51.58,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Who could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:55.42,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Tsuyoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:56.42,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Mizuho?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.17,0:13:04.22,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I... Ever since the entrance ceremony, I've liked you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.22,0:13:08.51,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be just friends anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:10.31,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Mizuho.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.73,0:13:16.19,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Tsuyoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.60,0:13:17.90,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:19.77,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,N-No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.65,0:13:22.28,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Mayumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:23.28,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Could this letter be from her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:27.07,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Today, I'll go out and have fun with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:36.08,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:38.96,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Mayumi wouldn't write a letter to express her feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.21,0:13:44.09,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I can't help it, so I'll go out with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:45.30,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.63,0:13:46.97,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Come give me the kiss of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:54.27,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.27,0:13:55.48,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Definitely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.48,0:13:58.40,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Tsuyoshi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.94,0:14:01.36,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,It's no good to keep secrets from your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.77,0:14:02.48,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.98,0:14:03.73,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Oh!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.11,0:14:05.69,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,L-Love letter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:07.70,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:08.32,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,– No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:08.61,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,– Give it back!\N– No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.61,0:14:09.24,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,– Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.49,0:14:10.28,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Hey?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.37,0:14:16.71,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:34.93,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.68,0:14:37.02,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,If anyone picks that up, that's it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.56,0:14:43.02,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:45.94,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Did you see a letter here somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:47.90,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,N-Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.07,0:14:49.65,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,It's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:54.28,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.74,0:14:58.33,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Ummm... You're Minamizato Ai from 2-A.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:14:59.58,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.83,0:15:02.42,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Geez... You checked all the underclassmen girls' names?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.79,0:15:03.67,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.42,0:15:07.71,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What we're looking for is his lov...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.71,0:15:09.22,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Argh! Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.43,0:15:14.14,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.43,0:15:17.77,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me that you're gonna go after that girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:20.02,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,How could I do that to a younger student?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.02,0:15:22.98,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,With you, it's hard to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.69,0:15:26.32,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:28.65,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,That girl was the one who wrote the letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:34.87,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What am I going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:38.37,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I have to return this to Yamaguchi-senpai quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.21,0:15:46.88,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Senpai's desk is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:52.13,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What is up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.68,0:15:53.72,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I... I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.22,0:15:55.01,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.39,0:15:56.60,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:16:00.18,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You made a mistake about the class room, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:03.94,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I do that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:07.02,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,This one time in 2nd year...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.40,0:16:12.82,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I didn't even know until the teacher was calling roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.43,0:16:37.10,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I'm really wiped out today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.27,0:16:42.98,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.18,0:16:43.60,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:46.27,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Mmm... Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.56,0:16:48.90,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Don't hide it from me. You're a bad liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.82,0:16:55.20,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,If you don't tell me the truth, then I'll do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.36,0:16:55.57,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,– Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.57,0:16:55.91,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,– Like this, hurry and tell me.\N– Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:56.28,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,– Like this, hurry and tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.28,0:16:56.91,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,– Miyuki-chan!\N– Like this, hurry and tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:57.24,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,– Like this, hurry and tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.24,0:16:58.03,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,– Alright, alright!\N– Like this, hurry and tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.03,0:16:59.12,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,– Alright, alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:01.24,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:07.08,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.08,0:17:09.42,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,How am I going to return it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.50,0:17:12.21,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You're not honest, Ai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.71,0:17:13.13,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.59,0:17:15.68,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Ai, what you're really worried about is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.18,0:17:19.85,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Who Yamaguchi-senpai's dating, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.97,0:17:23.73,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Take a step before you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.43,0:17:27.19,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,This is what you need now, Ai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.31,0:17:30.94,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,If you don't take a step forward,\Nyou'll never get anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.73,0:17:35.20,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,But then again, it is Yamaguchi-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.49,0:17:37.11,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I don't really want you getting mixed up with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.37,0:17:45.37,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.35,0:18:03.06,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Minatsu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.56,0:18:04.56,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,The next one is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.97,0:18:05.68,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.98,0:18:07.39,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Minatsu-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:08.81,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.10,0:18:10.02,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Minoru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:12.48,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,No matter how much you help, I won't pay you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:14.98,Hardsub,,0,0,10,,{\an8\fs23}Notes: Coffee shop owners are typiclly addressed as "Master" in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:14.98,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You are really mean, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:18.91,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I can't afford to to pay three people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.49,0:18:21.37,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, Tsuyoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:22.83,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.03,0:18:24.70,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I'm going out for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.83,0:18:26.50,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.66,0:18:27.75,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You can't just leave all of a sudden!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.58,0:18:30.50,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Minoru will be happy to do the rest today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.71,0:18:31.25,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.70,0:19:03.03,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:14.59,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,If you don't take a step forward,\Nyou'll never get anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:31.19,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.53,0:19:43.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Did I get the place wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.42,0:20:01.80,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.39,0:20:05.85,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Ai-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:12.52,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You don't really have to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.10,0:20:14.73,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,So-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.65,0:20:17.23,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.15,0:20:19.94,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Ai-chan, you were the one who wrote that letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:20.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.05,0:20:43.51,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.84,0:20:44.13,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:47.80,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I picked this up at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.26,0:20:49.97,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I didn't know how to return this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.72,0:20:51.72,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.94,0:20:56.98,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.68,0:21:33.73,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,An underclassman, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.46,0:22:01.29,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.64,0:22:54.31,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.18,0:22:57.85,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,at that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.48,0:23:01.81,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,was I okay when senpai touched me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.31,0:23:04.02,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.91,0:23:21.21,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,How was the date?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.67,0:23:22.58,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,She came.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.71,0:23:24.13,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,She's absolutely cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.34,0:23:26.75,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.67,0:23:28.76,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,This is the evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.55,0:23:31.38,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What? Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.80,0:23:33.30,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Because I...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.47,0:23:34.01,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.93,0:23:35.35,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.35,0:23:37.35,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.35,0:23:39.18,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You'd better tell me everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.52,0:23:39.98,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Minoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.08,0:24:00.91,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I wonder who senpai's date was...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.96,0:24:11.47,Hardsub,,0,0,10,,{\an8}tsukan de Oh! A!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.96,0:24:11.47,Hardsub,,0,0,10,,Catch it. Oh! Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.67,0:24:13.22,Hardsub,,0,0,10,,{\an8}sono te ni Sha! Sha!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.67,0:24:13.22,Hardsub,,0,0,10,,By that hand. Sha! Sha!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.43,0:24:16.30,Hardsub,,0,0,10,,{\an8}himitsu no chikara
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.43,0:24:16.30,Hardsub,,0,0,10,,The secret power.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.85,0:24:22.89,Hardsub,,0,0,10,,{\an8}kono omoi dake wa hanasanai
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.85,0:24:22.89,Hardsub,,0,0,10,,I won't let my this feeling go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.27,0:24:30.49,Hardsub,,0,0,10,,{\an8}moshi anata ga
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.27,0:24:30.49,Hardsub,,0,0,10,,If you
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.74,0:24:33.99,Hardsub,,0,0,10,,{\an8}kocchi mitara
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.74,0:24:33.99,Hardsub,,0,0,10,,look this side
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.20,0:24:40.04,Hardsub,,0,0,10,,{\an8}ku-ru na shisen de madowasuno
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.20,0:24:40.04,Hardsub,,0,0,10,,I will attract by your cool glance.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.16,0:24:44.42,Hardsub,,0,0,10,,Considerable
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.54,0:24:47.88,Hardsub,,0,0,10,,{\an8}shai na egao
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.54,0:24:47.88,Hardsub,,0,0,10,,shy smiling face.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.04,0:24:53.93,Hardsub,,0,0,10,,{\an8}sotto misereba seikoune
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.04,0:24:53.93,Hardsub,,0,0,10,,Show him quietly is the successful way right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.47,0:25:00.64,Hardsub,,0,0,10,,{\an8}yukkurimada yume wo tsumugitai
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.47,0:25:00.64,Hardsub,,0,0,10,,I still want to hold my dream inside of myself slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.39,0:25:05.35,Hardsub,,0,0,10,,{\an8}tashikana mono hora chikakuni
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.39,0:25:05.35,Hardsub,,0,0,10,,The certain thing is very close to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.48,0:25:08.90,Hardsub,,0,0,10,,{\an8}to wo nobashite
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.48,0:25:08.90,Hardsub,,0,0,10,,Extend your hand.
